OL,3,CChannel Islands concerned over
OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour due to alcohol
OL,6,FMore than 85% of people in Jersey and
OL,7,FGuernsey who responded to a new survey
OL,8,Fare concerned about antisocial
OL,9,Fbehaviour due to alcohol.
OL,11,FOver 2,600 residents from the
OL,12,FBailiwicks answered Island Global
OL,13,FResearch's questions on alcohol
OL,14,Fconsumption.
OL,16,FThe survey aims to understand people's
OL,17,Fviews towards the impact of alcohol on
OL,18,Fislanders and measures that could
OL,19,Freduce the harm it causes.
