OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour due to alcohol
OL,6,FWhile around a third of respondents
OL,7,Fthought it was socially acceptable to
OL,8,Fget drunk, a similar amount also
OL,9,Fbelieve alcohol consumption by another
OL,10,Fperson has negatively impacted their
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,FOne Jersey resident wants "more
OL,14,Fsupport to be provided easily and in
OL,15,Fvarious ways to people who struggle
OL,16,Ffrom their alcohol consumption and
OL,17,Ftheir families".
