OL,3,CChannel Islands concerned over
OL,4,Cantisocial behaviour due to alcohol
OL,6,FIn Jersey, 56% of respondents said
OL,7,Fthat more should be done to reduce the
OL,8,Fharm caused by alcohol - that figure
OL,9,Ffell slightly to 52% in Guernsey.
OL,11,FThe survey also asked respondents how
OL,12,Fharm could be reduced through
OL,13,Fpreventative steps such as more
OL,14,Fcontrols on alcohol promotion and how
OL,15,Fproducts are presented in shops.
OL,17,FMore than 80% of those surveyed from
OL,18,Fboth islands believe that showing the
OL,19,Funits of alcohol on a product's
OL,20,Fpackaging should be a legal
OL,21,Frequirement.
