OL,6,FHowever, some respondents believe that
OL,7,Fit is on the individual to make their
OL,8,Fown decisions with the survey saying
OL,9,Fthat many did not want a 'nanny state'.
OL,11,FOne Guernsey resident commented:
OL,12,F"People are old enough to make up
OL,13,Ftheir own minds and take
OL,14,Fresponsibility for themselves."
OL,16,FA Jersey respondent also reflected:
OL,17,F"Having been married to an alcoholic,
OL,18,Fno amount of government control
OL,19,Finitiatives will stop someone drinking.
