OL,6,F"In some cases, it makes it worse
OL,7,F(...) Raising taxes on alcohol doesn't
OL,8,Fstop the person drinking, but it has
OL,9,Fan impact on the family because they
OL,10,Fhave less money to live on."
OL,12,FIsland Global Research's survey is
OL,13,Fpart of a wider health series, with
OL,14,Ffuture surveys to look into smoking,
OL,15,Fvaping and cannabis use.
